        <item>
            <title>Threads 分享真入境处来电惨被 3 次 cut 线，网民回应：经常被当成诈骗电话</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Threads]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[入境处]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[诈骗电话]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268930</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信各位朋友都曾经收过骗徒冒充入境处的诈骗电话，因此大家一接到声称来自入境处的来电均会有戒心。早前有网民在 Threads 分享指，友人曾经多次接获声称来自入境处的电话，误以为是诈骗电话，因此多次收线，直至对方哀求「我求下你唔好收线呀，求下你听一听我讲先」，再交代来电源由，友人才警醒是真入境处来电。</p><div class="-ml-3 w-screen md:ml-0 md:w-full"><div class="placeholder-hk01"><div class="lazyload-wrapper "></div></div></div><blockquote id="ig-tp-DBASRMtTT_d" class="text-post-media" style="background: #FFF; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 540px; margin: 1px; min-width: 270px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px); border: 1px solid #00000026;" data-text-post-permalink="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015/post/DBASRMtTT_d" data-text-post-version="0"><div style="padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><div style="display: block; height: 32px; width: 32px; padding-bottom: 20px;"></div><div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; color: #999999; font-weight: 400; padding-bottom: 4px;">Post by @vanmama1015</div><div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; color: #000000; font-weight: 600;">View on Threads</div></div></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.threads.net/embed.js"></script></p><p class="break-words">网民 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015">vanmama1015</a> 在 Threads 上分享了一件有关入境处来电的趣事，表示朋友曾接获声称是入境处职员的电话，对方表示：「X 小姐你好，我系香港入境处&#8230;&#8230;」，未待电话另一方说完，朋友就认为是诈骗电话，随即收线。</p><p class="break-words">其后对方再次来电，语气焦急的表示自己的确是香港入境处，恳求朋友不要收线：「你系 X 小姐吗？我真系香港入境处呀，你唔好收线先&#8230;.」，但朋友亦不予理会，直接收线。</p><p class="break-words">最后该电话第三次来电，以非常焦急的语气表示自己「真系入境处」，更哀求朋友不要收线：「求下你听一听我讲先」，然后快速交代问朋友是否正在申请（外籍家庭佣工姓名）来港一事，朋友才警觉的确是真入境处来电。</p><p><a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015">vanmama1015</a> 最后笑指入境处职员比做 cold call（陌生来电销售）更惨，随时被「cut 线」拒绝次数更多。下面有网民回应，表示有朋友在入境处工作，真的经常被当成诈骗电话「cut 线」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1-694x210.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="210" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1-694x210.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1.jpg 803w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@cyan421/post/DBAfKozSR9q">Threads</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.immd.gov.hk/publications/a_report_2021/tc/chapter2.html">入境事务处 2021 年年报</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@vanmama1015/post/DBASRMtTT_d">vanmama1015@Threads</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">「微信保险」诈骗电话 Cut 线会打来问原因　连登网民分享对付骗徒新招</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/14/immigration-department-was-identified-as-scam-call/life-tech/social-network/">Threads 分享真入境处来电惨被 3 次 cut 线，网民回应：经常被当成诈骗电话</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
